{"tid":2021311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【中超】為佳兆業友賽恒大 載偉浚攻入一球","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T01:54:54.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"98d2fae4b260b7f0d169add938e81f3c98eef033","tid":2021311,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"香港出生、擁有英籍的戴偉浚目前正於中國的深圳佳兆業試腳，該會上周六（16日）與廣州恒大友賽，戴偉浚再獲上陣機會，且攻入一球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200517/DRROAPNFOXVFEMT4E4BGGCO3U4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200517%2FDRROAPNFOXVFEMT4E4BGGCO3U4%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=701a9898\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200517%2FDRROAPNFOXVFEMT4E4BGGCO3U4%2F&h=0bf1fc11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200517/DRROAPNFOXVFEMT4E4BGGCO3U4/</a>"},{"pid":"2d4d0ad05188f40e26367223c38cebb833908d30","tid":2021311,"uid":209225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主五毛狗<br />\n唔使回</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f4134d776f310202f178df68574342bb140f0980","tid":2021311,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4d0ad05188f40e26367223c38cebb833908d30","tid":2021311,"uid":209225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主五毛狗<br />\n唔使回</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"糖哥 我幾時變埋五毛狗？ <br />\n比次機會得唔得？😭😭😭"},{"pid":"a4c98615cee3a31cf162815af7854c886bfe3572","tid":2021311,"uid":73381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"希望浚狗第一場就斷腳 斷完左腳斷右腳<br />\n斷完右腳斷左前腳 斷完左前腳斷右前腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251e3d4ad17c5f4867dd0addfb1a5ae0f4518b4f","tid":2021311,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"對於他的愛徙戴偉浚，兩年前因報稱受傷而拒絕港隊徵召，卻被發現到中國U21足球隊跟隨操練一段時間，遭大批網民抨擊，認為戴偉浚是假傷。李健和為愛徒護航：「佢本身嗰邊嘅聯賽踢得比較密啲，甚至係冇乜時間返香港。同埋香港隊徵召佢嘅時間，相信佢都有衡量過香港隊比賽嘅重要性有幾大，如果係世界盃外圍賽、亞洲盃嗰啲，佢可能會比較覺得重視啲囉！佢又喺外國，又要特登飛返嚟踢，所以職業足球員其實都係會取捨比賽重要性。」至於戴偉浚選擇踢香港隊還是中國隊，和哥坦言：「冇人控制到。」<br />\n<br />\n效力過英超球隊狼隊U23的20歲戴偉浚，據聞已加盟將遞補踢中超的深圳佳兆業，更被球隊助教馬達洛尼指，有潛力成為中國國家隊未來希望。戴偉浚與和哥感情要好，由以前東方青年軍，到現在成為職業足球員，兩人一直有保持聯絡。和哥讚賞戴偉浚服從性高、勤力、天份優厚，尤其是傳波準確度特別高，有今日成就是實至名歸。"},{"pid":"1f16948e8007e954d4116d1e5214ea9aa7e04464","tid":2021311,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"有潛力成為中國國家隊未來希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdff42cb6c52c851f3e55640bcbc4477b07e0611","tid":2021311,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f16948e8007e954d4116d1e5214ea9aa7e04464","tid":2021311,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"有潛力成為中國國家隊未來希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/